Episodes.Title: Pilot
Episodes.Plot: In the series premiere of "Awkward", Jenna Hamilton finds out that getting the boy of her dreams isn't all it's cracked up to be. When a mysterious letter leads to a misunderstanding of epic proportions, Jenna realizes that her new stigma might be her ticket to social visibility.
Episodes.ParentalRatingReason: M Sex scenes and offensive language
Episodes.GuestStars: Jessica Lu, Mike Faiola, Greer Grammer

Episodes.GuestStars: Jessica Lu, Mike Faiola, Greer Grammer, Jesse Heiman, Catfish Jean, Anna Akana, Evan Arnold, Keith Pillow

Episodes.Plot: Jenna's sixteenth birthday isn't very sweet as she suffers one embarrassing experience after the next.
